**Adding New Engine Endpoints:**

When adding a new Python engine endpoint, add the corresponding function to `lib/engine/client.ts`:

```typescript
// 1. Define request/response interfaces (snake_case for Python API)
interface MyFeatureRequest {
  param_one: string;
  param_two: number;
}

interface MyFeatureResponse {
  result_value: string;
  tokens_used: number;
}

// 2. Create the typed function with camelCase interface
export async function callMyFeature(request: { paramOne: string; paramTwo: number }): Promise<{
  resultValue: string;
  tokensUsed: number;
}> {
  const response = await callEngine<MyFeatureRequest, MyFeatureResponse>(
    '/api/v1/my-feature/endpoint',
    {
